translated: Eneström, Carl Adolf, landowner, Håkantorp, born on September 16th, 1882 in Håkantorp, Levene. Son of landowner Oscar E. and Augusta Isländer. Married in 1909 to Gudrun Arveschoug. Children: Per Ludvig born in 1910, Gunvor in 1911, Barbro in 1913, Sonja in 1916, Anders in 1922, and Monica in 1926. Educated at Vänersborg elementary school and Lund's private elementary school. Completed studies in agriculture at Alnarps lantbruksskola in 1906. Became administrator of Håkantorp's estate in 1906 and owned the estate from 1922. Vice-chairman of Skara stiftsnd since 1935, chairman of Levene municipal council until 1946, vice-chairman of Levene school board, vice-chairman of Sysitem A-B in Lidköping, chairman of Vara-Slättens Spannmålslagerhusfören., auditor for Älvsborg Hypothecary Association in Gothenburg, member of the board of Skaraborgs Lantarbetsgivareforening, chairman of Levene Dairy Association, chairman of Skaraborgs Lantbruksförening for lowland cattle breeding, and dedicated member of the board of Avelisföreningen for lowland cattle breeding from 1948. Awarded RVO and PatrGM.
